products.title: Warpaints Fanatic: Washes Paint Set - Combo
products.body_html:
Create perfectly shaded and colour toned miniatures with The Warpaints Fanatic Washes Set.
  • 10 Washes ranging from a rich Dark Tone to a vibrant Dark Red Tone
  • Wow your opponents with impressive details and realistic shading
  • Can be used directly from the bottle 
  • Get the Warpaints Fanatic Wash Paint Set PLUS and a Basecoating Brush

products.title: Quickshade Washes: Paint Set
products.body_html:
These Washes are probably the best in the hobby and will get you perfect shading every time plus the option of adding a colour tone to your miniatures.
  • 11 x Quickshade Washes
  • Perfect shading every time
  • 100% colour match to the corresponding Quickshade Varnish cans

products.title: Quickshade Dip: Strong Tone
products.body_html:
An entirely unique product on the market, it will enable you to paint your the army of your dreams in no time at all.
  • Specifically designed and engineered to work with 10-28mm. miniatures.
  • Finally, a product which will shade your army perfectly and is fantastically easy to use.
  • Dont panic! but get ready for amazing shading no matter your painting level.
  • Painting armies of miniatures to fantastic results has never been easier.

products.title: Warpaints Washes: Strong Tone
products.body_html: This Quickshade Wash is a perfect match of the Quickshade of the same name. Ideal for adding extra shading, touching up mistakes and for washing the whole of the model.

products.title: Warpaints Washes: Blue Tone
products.body_html:
The Quickshade Blue Tone Wash is loaded with heavy blue pigment in the popular Warpaints ink resin base. Use on top of white for an instant blue toned and shaded miniature or on top of blue colours for extra depth and shading.

Shading and colour toning in one wash.

products.title: Warpaints Washes: Flesh Wash
products.body_html:
Quickshade Wash: Flesh Wash has the perfect tone for shading lighter flesh tones. Be it Dwarf, Elf, Historical or Sci-Fi miniature, the high-quality Quickshade series offers the best in conventional shading available to the wargaming scene. Apply base colour and give it a wash with the Flesh Tone – and the miniature comes to life.

Perfect results – every time.

products.title: Warpaints Washes: Mid Brown
products.body_html: The Quickshade Washes share the same type of extra heavy pigment which makes them formidable for adding shading and colourful effects to a miniature. There are 11 different toned Quickshade Washes in the range.

products.title: Warpaints Washes: Green Tone
products.body_html:
The Quickshade Green Tone Wash is loaded with deep green and heavier dark pigment in the popular Warpaints ink resin base. Use on top of white for an instant green toned and shaded miniature or on top of all greens, Necrotic Flesh or even Barbarian Flesh for the putrid look. As all the Quickshade Washes, it looks stunning on a metal primer for that Nurgle look.

Shading and colour toning in one wash.

products.title: Warpaints Washes: Purple Tone
products.body_html:
The Quickshade Purple Tone Wash is loaded with deep Purple and heavier dark pigment in the popular Warpaints ink resin base. Use on top of white for an instant purple toned and shaded miniature or on top of purple, red or blue for extra depth and shading. 

As all the Quickshade Washes, it looks stunning on a metal primer for that Slaaneshi look.

Shading and colour toning in one wash.

products.title: Warpaints Washes: Red Tone
products.body_html:
The Quickshade Red Tone Wash is loaded with red and heavy black pigment in the popular Warpaints ink resin base. Use on top of white for an instant red toned and shaded miniature or on top of yellow, orange or red colours for extra depth and shading.

As all the Quickshade Washes, it looks stunning on a metal primer, giving it an evil Khorne look.

Shading and colour toning in one wash.
